<plot>A young woman works in a school restaurant. It's the last day before the summer holidays. She asks for a money advance to be able to take her daughter on vacation, but it is refused. This film shows the struggle of this woman to get the sum that will allow her daughter's summer not to be wasted.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?332683</url></doc>
